## 3. Creation Order (Bottom-Up Dependencies)

Create files in this sequence to ensure each file's imports are satisfied before the files that depend on them:

1. `package.json` — no code deps
2. `openclaw.plugin.json` — no code deps
3. `src/types.ts` — imports from `./runtime-api.js` (type-only); can stub initially
4. `runtime-api.ts` — pure re-export barrel, no local deps
5. `src/runtime.ts` — imports `runtime-api.js`
6. `src/normalize.ts` — imports `./types.js`
